data.description: Don't miss this like-new Elgin home! This property features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, on two city lots. Beautiful kitchen with granite countertops and open concept living area. Additional features include a water softener and a reverse osmosis filtration system for drinkable alkaline water. Fenced backyard, laundry room, and an electric fireplace. Walking distance to the Elgin Schools. Call today to schedule a showing of this property. Owner is a licensed Oklahoma Real Estate agent agent.
